    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-06-13T03:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-06-13T03:00:00-05:00" n="889"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d889">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.248/550: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ankara</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-06-13T11:00:00+03:00"
                            >June 13, 1942—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 5:14 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>590. Fourth Liberator referred to in my 585, June 12, 8 p.m., appears to have
                    succeeded in reaching Syrian territory.</p>
                <p>The Turkish General Staff informed me this morning that fifth Liberator landed at
                    Arifiye with 3 of the crew injured and that a sixth American airplane as yet
                    unidentified as to type has landed at Yalova with crew of 3 of whom 1 is
                    dead.</p>
                <pb facs="0803" n="791" xml:id="pg_791"/>
                <p>General staff also states that it has received an as yet unconfirmed report that
                    a seventh American airplane has landed at Mudanya.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Cairo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Steinhardt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
